{
  "text": "Dessert banana and plantain (Musa sp.) are the fourth most important staple food crops in the world after rice, wheat and maize [CITATION_1] . They are also important sources of income for many smallholder SubSaharan Africa farmers (FAOSTAT, 2012) .",
  "citation_candidates": [
